{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"824d4fc8bd","title":"转发彭德怀关于征收营业税的调查报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cc484a98b4","index":0,"year":1948,"month":2,"day":null,"articleId":"824d4fc8bd"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji24","name":"毛泽东全集第24卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji24.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji24":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"cbd035d8bb","type":"paragraph","text":"转发彭德怀关于征收营业税的","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"824d4fc8bd"},{"id":"c6c213fcdf","type":"paragraph","text":"调查报告的批语","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"824d4fc8bd"},{"id":"9f02f7b4c9","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年2月）各地对于工商业的税收政策的内容及其结果如何，完全没有或很少向中央作报告。据所知的远不完全的材料看来，极端危险的带有破坏性的既不符合于正确的经济观点，也不符合于正确的财政爱点的冒险主义的税收政策是存在着的。这种冒险主义的政策必须加以纠正。望各中央局、中央分局认真检查一次对工商业的税收政策，以其结果报告中央[1]彭德怀2月14日给中共中央西北局并报中央的报合中说：招我们在资物不够抵偿，实际上只收到9石，约占1947年全年营业剂润60%。1947","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"824d4fc8bd"}],"page":{"id":"9b3339d0a7","publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"824d4fc8bd","start":122,"end":122}}}},"__N_SSG":true}